    <h3>Scenario Builder</h3>
    <p>Create multi-sensor alarms for any scenario in your plant. The Scenario Builder allows operators to create multi-sensor alarms with DCS and non-DCS data that Streamlyne will automatically evaluate, and then alert the likelihood of that specific scenario occurring (ie. flaring, hydrates). A scenario can include just one sensor or a string of sensors that lead up to an event/ scenario. Now you can track in real time the progression of any event and take action faster.
    </p>
