    <h3>Flaring</h3>
    <p>Unplanned flaring is a drain on both profitability and product, can be hazardous to the surrounding environment, and create red flags to government. With Streamlyne you can identify the pathway of “triggers” (sensors) that are involved in any flaring event to help you identify when a flare might take place. This allows you and your plant to be proactive instead of reactive, reducing costs and unknown outcomes.
    </p>
  </div>

